OL,6,GThe 40th anniversary of BBC breakfast
OL,7,GTV was celebrated beautifully. From a
OL,8,Gdesign fan's point of view, there was
OL,9,Gmuch to enjoy.
OL,11,FBringing back the old analogue clock
OL,12,Ffor the morning was a lovely touch. The
OL,13,Fmodern take on the original Breakfast
OL,14,FTime astons was beautifully stylish.
OL,16,FBut there is also a story of how the
OL,17,FBBC finally came to find the right
OL,18,Fformat for breakfast TV after a long
OL,19,Fjourney.
OL,21,FBreakfast Time was an immediate success
OL,22,Fin its early days.
OL,3,CReflections on the history of BBC
OL,4,Cbreakfast TV
