OL,6,FThis relaunch is sometimes forgotten
OL,7,Fnow as the name remained.
OL,9,FWhatever happened behind-the-scenes,
OL,10,Fthe subsequent changes into BBC
OL,11,FBreakfast News in 1989 and Breakfast in
OL,12,Fits modern form in 2000 seemed
OL,13,Fevolutionary from the viewer's
OL,14,Fperspective. There was no great
OL,15,Fcontroversy on either occasion.
OL,17,FAfter 2000 the atmosphere gradually got
OL,18,Fwarmer and that old friendly atmosphere
OL,19,Fwas restored.
OL,21,FBreakfast today is a news programme
OL,22,Frooted in the BBC's journalism.
OL,3,CReflections on the history of BBC
OL,4,Cbreakfast TV
